Class PreisEintrag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pizza.CMModel.DBConnect
      • com.pizza.CMModel.PreisEintrag

  • public class PreisEintrag
extends DBConnect

    Models the Preis Entry of the Preis Table

    The PreisEintrag class is used to model the Preis Table of the database. In addition to getters and setter of the corresponding fields, there is a method used to store a new entry to the table.
